        {
            "author_association": "CONTRIBUTOR",
            "body": "> If we promote setting these options within lsp.start/config it has the disadvantage that authors of plugins will likely not add .luarc.json files which makes the life worse for contributors who also work on lua projects outside the neovim space. (I'm certainly guilty of that)\r\n\r\nI think it's better to mention it in [Lua plugin guide](https://github.com/neovim/neovim/pull/29073)",
